??It s very convenient for visitors to enjoy most Universiade events by Taipei MRT.  Let s take the Red Line today.??  It starts its service from the bank of gleaming Tamsui River to the famous Shilin Night market  and then all the way to the Taipei 101 skyscraper. It allows you arrange a getaway along the line in addition to attending the events.  These are the Universiade events that can be reached with the Red Line:  1. Yuanshan (R14): Billiards?? 2. Zhishan (R17): Baseball ? and Diving 3. Tamsui (R28): Weightlifting??  MRT passes can be conveniently purchased at all entrances of each station.??  For the competition Schedule: https://goo.gl/rD7xup Tickets Information: https://tickets.2017.taipei/  For more information about Taipei MRT  please visit?? http://english.metro.taipei

In oriental cultures  the hollow inside of bamboo epitomizes intellects  virtues – modesty  honesty and decency.   Designed with the  Competition with Decency  concept from Confucius s book  The Analects  in mind  the cauldron torch employs elements such as the base of Taiwan s traditional hexagram bamboo pattern and the burner cone with bamboo weaving features shaped by advanced five-axis laser cutters.  The torch is now being passed in Taiwan on a   LOVE   path. You can follow the path at https://goo.gl/rXn594  ?? More Torch：https://goo.gl/Fp8Uaj ?? Closing Ceremony Tickets！http://tickets.2017.taipei

Stretching from Xindian to Songshan  the Green Line of Taipei MRT brings you from the Bitan (Jade Lake) attraction to Raohe Night Market – one of Taipei s street delicacy destinations.??????  Of course  the Universiade events are too exciting to miss out on. So hurry up  embark on the Green Line to attend the following events:  1. Gongguan (G07): volleyball  at the National Taiwan University Sports Center.?? 2. Taipei Arena (G17): basketball  at the Taipei Arena; athletics  at the Taipei Stadium; badminton  at the Taipei Gymnasium.???????  MRT passes can be conveniently purchased at all entrances of each station. ??  For the competition Schedule: https://goo.gl/rD7xup Tickets Information: https://tickets.2017.taipei/  For more information about Taipei MRT  please visit ?? http://english.metro.taipei

?? The domestic torch relay started today!!   ? The core concept of the relay is “ LOVE = Taipei ”.   The design also symbolizes connections among the 22 cities and counties of Taiwan through love.  After being lit at the top of Mt. Jade  the relay route will consist of four stages  one for each letter of LOVE.  ?? For more Torch Relay https://goo.gl/ss6wr1 ??
